{"data":[{"name":"102:1","price":"竞赛富庶，已使你们疏忽，","arabic":"أَلۡهَىٰكُمُ ٱلتَّكَاثُرُ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6169,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"alhākumu al-takāthuru ","translations":["Diverts you","the competition to increase","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["alhākumu","al-takāthuru",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1350],[2,1350,3315]]}},{"name":"102:2","price":"直到你们去游坟地。","arabic":"حَتَّىٰ زُرۡتُمُ ٱلۡمَقَابِرَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6170,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"ḥattā zur'tumu al-maqābira ","translations":["Until","you visit","the graves","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["ḥattā","zur'tumu","al-maqābira",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,930],[2,930,1800],[3,1800,3955]]}},{"name":"102:3","price":"真的，你们将来就知道了。","arabic":"كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6171,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā sawfa taʿlamūna ","translations":["Nay","Soon","you will know","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","sawfa","taʿlamūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,1570],[3,1570,5275]]}},{"name":"102:4","price":"然后，真的，你们将来就知道了。","arabic":"ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6172,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma kallā sawfa taʿlamūna ","translations":["Then","nay","Soon","you will know","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","kallā","sawfa","taʿlamūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1620],[2,1620,2530],[3,2530,3320],[4,3320,6665]]}},{"name":"102:5","price":"真的，假若你们有真知灼见，〔你们必不疏忽〕，","arabic":"كَلَّا لَوۡ تَعۡلَمُونَ عِلۡمَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6173,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā law taʿlamūna ʿil'ma al-yaqīni ","translations":["Nay","If","you know","(with) a knowledge","(of) certainty","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","law","taʿlamūna","ʿil'ma","al-yaqīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,960],[2,960,1270],[3,1270,2520],[4,2520,3140],[5,3140,6505]]}},{"name":"102:6","price":"你们必定看见火狱，","arabic":"لَتَرَوُنَّ ٱلۡجَحِيمَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6174,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"latarawunna al-jaḥīma ","translations":["Surely you will see","the Hellfire","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["latarawunna","al-jaḥīma",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2230],[2,2230,5995]]}},{"name":"102:7","price":"然后，你们必亲眼看见它。","arabic":"ثُمَّ لَتَرَوُنَّهَا عَيۡنَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6175,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma latarawunnahā ʿayna al-yaqīni ","translations":["Then","surely you will see it","(with the) eye","(of) certainty","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","latarawunnahā","ʿayna","al-yaqīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1100],[2,1100,3870],[3,3870,4450],[4,4450,7995]]}},{"name":"102:8","price":"在那日，你们必为恩泽而被审问。","arabic":"ثُمَّ لَتُسۡـَٔلُنَّ يَوۡمَئِذٍ عَنِ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6176,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma latus'alunna yawma-idhin ʿani al-naʿīmi ","translations":["Then","surely you will be asked","that Day","about","the pleasures","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","latus'alunna","yawma-idhin","ʿani","al-naʿīmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1580],[2,1580,3839],[3,3839,5159],[4,5159,5639],[5,5639,11874]]}}],"chapter":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur","Chapter At-Takathur","Takathur","Surah Takathur","Chapter Takathur","At Takathur","Surah At Takathur","Chapter At Takathur","Surah 102","Chapter 102","The Rivalry","التكاثر"],"version":{"key":"chinese_suliman","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"zh","version":"1.0.5","last_update":1710761004,"title":"Chinese Translation - Mohammed Suleiman","description":"Translation of the Qur’an meanings into Chinese, translated by Mohammed Makin, reviewed by Mohammed Suleiman with other specialists."}}